0:00:30.240,0:00:32.680
Ngationei kuti akadzikinurwa sei.

0:00:32.780,0:00:35.800
Ndiwe ani?!

0:00:35.800,0:00:38.200
Taurisa ! Taura!

0:00:38.200,0:00:39.160
Ndamupedza.

0:00:39.280,0:00:40.280
