0:02:54.240,0:02:55.200
Hongu.

0:02:55.200,0:02:57.760
Zvechokwadi, achaita bonde navo.

0:02:57.760,0:03:01.360
Kunyange mumakirabhu, anovawana

0:03:01.360,0:03:04.500
uye anozorara ne umwe umwe wavo.

0:03:04.500,0:03:06.300
Ndizvo zvatinoita.

0:03:06.300,0:03:07.800
Chii chawaita kumhuri yake?

0:03:07.800,0:03:11.080
Mhuri - ivo vaka vhiringika.

0:03:11.080,0:03:12.540
Kuvhiringidzika?

0:03:12.540,0:03:15.860
Iwe unogona kubvunza vabereki vake; hakuna munhu anogara navo zvakare.

0:03:15.860,0:03:17.400
Ndini ndoga anoda kugara navo

0:03:17.400,0:03:20.660
uye ini ndiri kutozvimanikidza kuti ndigare navo.

0:03:20.660,0:03:21.940
Handitombodi kugara navo

0:03:21.940,0:03:25.000
nokuti havanditenderi kuita zvinhu zvandinoda kuita -

0:03:25.000,0:03:31.560
zvakaita sekutevera vasikana, kuenda kumakirabhu, kunwa ne kusvuta.

0:03:31.560,0:03:33.800
Ndinosuwa hupenyu ihoho.

0:03:33.800,0:03:34.940
Ndiani murume uyu ari pedyo newe?

0:03:34.940,0:03:35.640
Vhura maziso ako!

0:03:35.640,0:03:37.280
Handigoni kuvhura maziso angu.

0:03:37.280,0:03:38.460
Ndiani murume uyu ari kuruboshwe rwako ?!

0:03:38.460,0:03:39.700
Handikwanise.

0:03:39.700,0:03:41.320
Changamire - magamuchirwa.

0:03:41.320,0:03:42.760
Uyu mukomana ndiani?

0:03:42.760,0:03:44.220
Iye ndiye gotwe mumhuri.

0:03:44.220,0:03:44.900
Gotwe renyu?

0:03:44.900,0:03:48.680
Ndangomuwana satani ndobva atora mukomana wacho.

0:03:48.680,0:03:51.520
Pashure pemakore maviri muunivhesiti, akatiza.

0:03:51.520,0:03:54.240
Chii chamugataure pamusoro pezve hupenyu hwake, kureurura kwake?

0:03:54.240,0:04:00.840
Zve chokwadi, mukomana uyu apera. Anonwa, zve madzimai ne madhiragi.

0:04:00.840,0:04:06.520
Onai maoko ake - uye zviri mumuviri wake wose.

0:04:06.520,0:04:08.360
Ndakamubata kuti ndimuunze pano.

0:04:08.360,0:04:11.700
Mwari Wamasimba Ose anzwa minyengetero yangu.

0:04:11.700,0:04:13.860
Madhamu - mukomana uyu ndiani?

0:04:13.860,0:04:14.740
Mwana wangu we gotwe.

0:04:14.740,0:04:17.040
Mungati kudii nezve mararamiro ake?

0:04:17.040,0:04:21.740
Hapana chakakosha chekunyora kumba pamusoro pake; iye munhu apedzwa.

0:04:21.740,0:04:25.980
Hakuna bhizinesi. Kuchikoro, haagoni kuzviita uye iye akasindimara.

0:04:25.980,0:04:30.780
Haaremekedze vakuru vake kana vabereki vake.

0:04:30.780,0:04:33.020
Takugamuchirai mukoma. Imi mungati chii pamusoro pake?

0:04:33.020,0:04:38.300
Muchidimbu, anonyadzisa munhu wose mumhuri; hapana kana chaanoita.

0:04:38.300,0:04:43.800
Haaremekedza vakuru vake; iye akatiza chikoro ndokurega zvose.

0:04:43.800,0:04:47.660
Anofambidzana ne madzima uye ane matatuu muviri wake wose. Iye anoenda ku makirabhu.

0:04:47.660,0:04:50.560
Zvakapinda mumusoro wake saizvozvo.

0:04:50.560,0:04:54.940
Iwe dhimoni - wakapinda sei maari?

0:04:54.940,0:05:02.420
Ndakamuona kubva pakuberekwa, kuti aizoshandira chinangwa changu -

0:05:02.420,0:05:10.640
kuvhiringidzika, hasha, ruchiva, zvipingamupinyi, kudzokera shure, ingozvitaura.

0:05:10.640,0:05:15.000
Mhuri iri mumhirizhonga; hakuna chinhu.

0:05:15.000,0:05:21.260
Hapana kana mwanakomana anogona kupa chero chinhu kana kunyange kuva nemotokari,

0:05:21.260,0:05:26.200
hatingambotaura nezvokupa vabereki vavo zvekudya; vose vakachona.

0:05:26.200,0:05:35.540
Kunyange hanzvadzi dzavo wanano dzavo marara.

0:05:35.540,0:05:38.320
Zvechokwadi, unoziva kuti ndiani akazviita.

0:05:38.320,0:05:39.160
Ndiani akazviita ?!

0:05:39.160,0:05:40.120
Unoziva.

0:05:40.120,0:05:44.920
Iwe dhimoni, mweya wakaipa - Jesu auya kuzosunungura murume uyu. Muzita ra Jesu;

0:05:44.920,0:05:48.800
Buda kunze! Buda! Muzita ra Jesu Kristu.

0:05:48.800,0:05:50.700
Buda! Iwe dhimoni rakaipa.

0:05:50.700,0:05:53.640
Moto mumuviri wako wose - muzita ra Jesu.

0:05:53.640,0:05:55.620
Moto pamatatuu aya emadhimoni.

0:05:55.680,0:05:57.120
Moto mumuviri wako wese.

0:05:57.120,0:05:59.560
Simba rimwe nerimwe redhimoni ngaripiswe.

0:05:59.620,0:06:05.320
Buda! Muzita ra Jeso Kristu.

0:06:05.320,0:06:07.280
Buda kunze iwe dhimoni.

0:06:07.280,0:06:10.440
Moto, muzita guru ra Jesu Kristu. Mumuviri wako wese nemaoko ako.

0:06:10.440,0:06:14.320
Moto!  moto we Mweya Mutsvene - muzita guru ra Jesu Kristu

0:06:14.380,0:06:16.700
Moto we Mweya Mutsvene -  muzita ra Jesu Kristu.

0:06:16.700,0:06:18.800
Muzita ra Jesu.

0:06:18.800,0:06:19.760
Ndinokutendai Ishe.

0:06:19.760,0:06:22.680
Simuka!

0:06:32.560,0:06:34.560
Huya.

0:06:35.620,0:06:38.160
Chii chaitika kwauri?

0:06:38.160,0:06:42.580
Unoyeuka zvawataura here?

0:06:42.580,0:06:45.820
Tarisai pano. Ndibaba vako here ava?

0:06:45.820,0:06:51.760
Hungu uye avo ndimai vangu ne hanzvadzi yangu mukuru.

0:06:51.760,0:06:57.820
Jesu adzingira kunze dhimoni iroro - mweya wakaipa, wakamuita kuti aite misikanzwa. Asununguka.

0:06:57.820,0:07:01.000
Ndapota - musamuyeuchidze zvakaitika kare. Zvekare zvake zvapfuura.

0:07:01.000,0:07:04.840
Jesu akusunungura. Enda undomutevera. Muzita ra Jesu.

0:07:04.840,0:07:05.700
Ameni

0:07:05.700,0:07:11.620
Ndinokutendai Jesu. Ndasununguka.

0:07:11.620,0:07:13.340
Ndinokutendai Tenzi.

0:07:13.340,0:07:15.580
Ndinokutendai Jesu. Mhuri yangu yasununguka.

0:07:15.580,0:07:18.640
Vanhu va Mwari - Emmanuel!

0:07:18.640,0:07:23.500
Zita rangu ndiBen Ezenwata. Ini ndinobva ku Imo State, asi ndinogara ku Togo nemhuri yangu.

0:07:23.500,0:07:27.460
Vanhu vakamira neni pano ndivo vakoma vangu, hanzvadzi dzangu ne vabereki -

0:07:27.460,0:07:31.740
