raiva re mweya wetsvina waive wakandigara - ngirozi yakawa.

0:07:40.100,0:07:53.400
Ngirozi yakawa yakandiratidza muitiro we zvinhu zvakasiyana siyana zvakaipa, zvakaita se kuenda kuma kirabhu,

0:07:53.400,0:08:00.040
kushandisa madhiragi, kunwa, kusvuta ne kunyorwa matatuu mumuviri wangu wose.

0:08:00.040,0:08:11.500
Zvose zvakatanga apo ndaiva mwana uye zvanga zvakadaro kubvira ipapo.

0:08:11.500,0:08:17.240
Zvaiva nekuda kwe marererwo andakaitwa nemhuri yangu ne hama dzakandipoteredza.

0:08:17.240,0:08:19.920
Ndakanga ndisiri kuwana rudo rwakanyanya ne kuchengetedzwa,

0:08:19.920,0:08:24.740
saka ndakakura ndiri munhu aive ne hutsinye kune vamwe pamwe ne kuita zvinhu ndakatsamwa.

0:08:24.740,0:08:27.860
Ndizvo zvandakapfuura ne mazviri nguva iyoyo.

0:08:27.860,0:08:31.120
Dhiyabhorosi akashandisa izvozvo se nzira yekupinda mandiri ne

0:08:31.120,0:08:38.320
kundiratidza tsika dzakawanda dzakaipa idzo ndakadzikinurwa kubva madziri kubva kuna wise man Racine.

0:08:38.320,0:08:41.980
Iwe wati wakanga wakagarwa ne mweya wengirozi yakawa.

0:08:41.980,0:08:46.880
Iwe unganyotso tsanangura here kuti dhimoni iri rakapinda mumuviri wako here? Uye basa raro raiva rei muupenyu hwako?

0:08:46.880,0:08:52.340
Nzira iyo dhimoni iri rakapinda nayo yaive ne kuburikidza nekuziva kwandakaita zve indaneti,

0:08:52.340,0:09:00.480
mafirimu, mimhanzi ne zvinhu zvakawanda zvepanyika zvaitika munharaunda yangu.

0:09:00.480,0:09:03.640
Izvi ndizvo zvinhu zvarakashandisa kupinda mandiri.

0:09:03.640,0:09:10.120
Nzira iyo dhimoni iri raitarisika yaiva hafu munhu, hafu mhuka.

0:09:10.120,0:09:19.680
Pakupinda mukati mangu, rakandiita kuti ndizive tsika dzakaipa dzakasiyana siyana uye marererwo angu zvakare akanga asina kunaka.

0:09:19.680,0:09:24.960
