0:09:49.020,0:09:56.460
Zvakandikuvadza chaizvo muzvidzidzo uye mu upenyu hwemhuri yangu.

0:09:56.460,0:09:59.280
Zvakakanganisa zvachose mativi ose ehupenyu hwangu nokuti

0:09:59.280,0:10:04.580
