0:10:04.580,0:10:10.520
Rakandishandisa se mukana wekupinda nawo mumhuri yangu nekukonzera kukanganisa kwakawanda.

0:10:10.520,0:10:15.920
Iwe wati dhimoni iri raizviratidza kwauri sehafu munhu, hafu- chisikwa.

0:10:15.920,0:10:20.880
Ndezvipi zvinhu zvaraizokuudza kuti uite uye raizviratidza sei kwauri usati wanunurwa?

0:10:20.880,0:10:27.080
Dhimoni raizviratidza kwandiri pandinenge ndatora madhiragi nepandaiteerera mimhanzi.

0:10:27.080,0:10:38.560
Pandaidhakwa pamusana pekutora madhiragi akawandisa, ndaigona kugara kwemazuva ndisingadye.

0:10:38.560,0:10:43.180
Ndinoteerera ku mimhanzi yenyika uye kuburikidza neizvozvo, ivo vakazotaudzana neni

0:10:43.180,0:10:50.100
nekundiudza zvekuita pandinenge ndavekuita sekurota apo ndinenge ndadhakwa.

0:10:50.100,0:10:53.580
Zvinhu zvakaita sei izvo madhimoni aya ayikukurudzira kuti uite?

0:10:53.580,0:11:04.200
Mhando yezvinhu izvo raindiudza kuti ndiite ndezve kushandisa madhiragi, kuenda kumakirabhu, kusaremekedza ne nungo.

