0:11:44.800,0:11:49.100
Saka, izvi ndidzo mhando yezvinhu izvo madhimoni aindiudza kuti ndiite apo ndakanga ndiri mumweya nawo.

0:11:49.100,0:11:50.560
Mukoma wedu ari kutaura nezve mamwe matatuu.

0:11:50.560,0:11:54.400
Kune kubwinya kwa Mwari - iwe ungatiratidza matatuu auri kutaura nezvawo pamuviri wako here?

0:11:54.400,0:11:58.860
Iwe wataura kuti chaizvoizvo madhimoni aya akashandisa matatuu aya senzira yekunyengera,

0:11:58.860,0:12:02.660
kunyengedza vanhu kuti vafunge kuti iwo angori matatuu zvawo, nepo muchokwadi chaicho

0:12:02.660,0:12:06.780
iwo aiva chimwe chinhu chinopfuura izvozvo - nzira yekupinzwa mazviri.

0:12:06.780,0:12:09.140
Tinongoda kuti iwe utiratidze matatuu aya.

0:12:09.140,0:12:13.520
Tirikubvunza mibvunzo iyi kuitira kuti tikwanise kudzidza kubva kuhama yedu,

0:12:13.520,0:12:16.500
