Iyi inongova nzira yekurega vanhu kunze uko kuti vafunge kuti ndeye chitendero, asi isiri.

0:12:36.880,0:12:41.160
Icho chiratidzo chete icho mweya yakaipa iri kushandisa.

0:12:41.160,0:12:46.620
Vamiririri vavo kunze uko - vanyori ve matatuu.

0:12:46.620,0:12:53.040
Pose paunoona munyori we tatuu iwe unoziva uti haasi matatuu nje,

0:12:53.040,0:12:57.720
