Vanhu vanofunga kuti inongova chiratidzo chechitendero, asi chaizvoizvo iyo ndiyo nzira yekupinzwa mazviri, uye chiratidzo chinobva kuna satani.

0:13:25.920,0:13:32.980
Matatu aya akasiyana-siyana amuri kuona pamuviri wangu ndeekuvharidzira.

0:13:32.980,0:13:38.600
Paiva pane imwe chete yakakosha, ngirozi yakagwa; yaida mapapiro ayo kuti ibhururke ichidzokera

0:13:38.600,0:13:43.940
Akanga achitaura kuti kuitira kuti awane mapapiro iwayo, aida zviratidzo izvozvo kuti zvive pandiri.

0:13:43.940,0:13:50.280
Ndaive ndichizonyorwa tatuu yemapapiro pamusana wangu - mapapiro makuru kwazvo.

0:13:50.280,0:13:59.720
Kuti awane mapapiro ake zvakare, aizowana izvozvo kuburikidza neni nekuisa chiratidzo chake kumusana wangu.

0:13:59.820,0:14:02.420
Tinovonga Mwari Wamasimba Ose nokuda kwe reururo ye mukoma wedu

0:14:02.420,0:14:06.280
Tinotenda kuti pane zvidzidzo zvakawanda zvinokosha zvatiri kudzidza kubva pane izvi.

0:14:06.280,0:14:11.340
Mukoma, wanga uchitaura pamusoro pevhidhiyo yezve munyika iyo yaune chekuita nezvayo,

0:14:11.340,0:14:16.820
semuyenzaniso; kushandisa indaneti, kuteerera nziyo dzenyika, kutamba mitambo yemavhidhiyo.

0:14:16.820,0:14:20.640
Ungagone here kutsanangura kuti mubayiro wakaipa waibva pazvinhu izvi muupenyu hwako ndewei,

0:14:20.640,0:14:24.020
uye satani aishandisa sei midziyo iyi kuti apinde muhupenyu hwako

0:14:24.020,0:14:28.460
uye zvechokwadi upenyu hwevechidiki pasi rose?

0:14:28.460,0:14:33.700
Nzira iyo mweya wakaipa uyu unobatana sei nevechidiki

0:14:33.700,0:14:37.760
iri kuburikidza neIndaneti ne mafirimu.

0:14:37.760,0:14:40.100
Zviri kunyanya kuburikidza neIndaneti.

0:14:40.100,0:14:45.200
Ndakazviwana nekuda kwe kuenda paIndaneti kuita zvinhu zvose zvemarudzi iwayo -

0:14:45.200,0:14:52.280
kutora mimwe mimhanzi ne kutarisa mifananidzo yevasina kupfeka.

0:14:52.280,0:14:56.040
Saka vechidiki vakawanda kunze uko vari kunyengerwa neizvi;

0:14:56.040,0:14:59.720
ivo vanopinzwa mazviri uye havazivi kuti chii chinoitika kwavari.

0:14:59.720,0:15:04.080
Vanozviona ivo vachiita zvinhu zvavanga vasingazivi kuti vaizoita.

0:15:04.080,0:15:07.320
Ndiwo matorero aanoita kuti avatonge.

0:15:07.320,0:15:11.000
Tinotenda kuti vechidiki pasi rose ne vanhu pano vari kunyatsoteerera kune hama yedu.

0:15:11.000,0:15:14.040
Tinotenda Mwari Wamasimba Ose kuti nhasi ari pano pa SCOAN.

0:15:14.040,0:15:19.060
Tiudzei mukoma, chii chakaitika pawakasvika pa SCOAN masvondo mashoma apfuura

0:15:19.060,0:15:22.240
ukagamuchira munyengetero musimba re Mweya Mutsvene.

0:15:22.240,0:15:27.040
Kuuya pano - munogona kubvunza vabereki vangu - kwaipikisana ne chido changu.

0:15:27.040,0:15:33.160
Vakatoita zvekundimanikidza kuti ndiuye pano uye ivo vakandimanikidza kuti nditange kuona Emmanuel TV.

0:15:33.160,0:15:41.140
Ndaigara ndichinzwa kuti pane chimwe chinhu pamusoro penzvimbo ino chandakanga ndisingadi kuve nechekuita nacho.

0:15:41.140,0:15:46.000
Pakupedzisira, ndakauya pano musi wa29 September nevabereki vangu.

0:15:46.000,0:15:48.100
Ndakanga ndisingambo zvitarisira.

0:15:48.100,0:15:52.220
Apo takaenda pamutsetse wekunamatirwa, wiseman Racine akandibata

0:15:52.220,0:15:58.220
uye ndipo pandakaita chadzimira nekusaziva

0:15:58.220,0:16:02.380
Zvakazotevera ndezvekuti ndakazozviwana ndimire kubva pasi.

0:16:02.380,0:16:05.540
Tinogona kuona pasikirini pano kuti mukoma wedu aidzikinurwa sei mukupera kwevhiki rapfuura.

0:16:05.540,0:16:11.780
Tiudze, kune kubwinya kwa Mwari, kubva pakununura kwako, ingopupura; ndezvipi zvachinja muupenyu hwako.

0:16:11.780,0:16:17.360
Iwe wati waive wapindwa muropa nekushandisa madhiragi, kusvuta, kunwa doro, nekuita zvefambidzana ne madzimai,

0:16:17.360,0:16:18.880
iwe wakanga wakapindwa muropa neIndaneti.

0:16:18.880,0:16:23.540
Tiudze zvachinja muhupenyu hwako mumavhiki maviri apfuura, kubva pakununurwa uku.

0:16:23.540,0:16:31.320
Zvange zvakaisvonaka uye zvinoshamisa nokuti kubuda kubva kune hupenyu ihwohwo ndizvo zvandaida.

0:16:31.320,0:16:37.640
Pakupedzisira, kuve akasununguka kubva mumweya wakaipa kwange kuchishamisa ne kunaka kwazvo kwandiri

0:16:37.640,0:16:40.500
nokuti ndinozviona ini ndichiita zvinhu zvandange ndisingaiti kare.

0:16:40.500,0:16:46.440
Zvino, ndinoteerera ku mimhanzi ye Vhangeri, kuverenga Bhaibheri ne nyengetera kwazvo.

0:16:46.440,0:16:51.680
Ndinozviona ndaka sununguka kubva kune zvinhu zvose izvozvo uye havi yaenda.

0:16:51.680,0:16:56.520
Handichina ruchiva rwevakadzi kana havi yekusvuta kana kushandisa madhiragi.

0:16:56.520,0:17:02.680
Handina chido chokuteerera ku mimhanzi yenyika kana kunyange mafirimu kana kutarisa mifananidzo ye vasina kupfeka.

0:17:02.680,0:17:06.880
Ini ndasununguka zvachose zvino uye ndazvarwa patsva. Rumbidzai Ishe!

0:17:06.880,0:17:12.660
Ameni. Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu kune kununurwa kwe mukoma wedu.

0:17:12.660,0:17:17.200
Tinotenda Jesu Kristu. Uye chekupedzisira, nderipi zano rako kune vanhu pasi pose,

0:17:17.200,0:17:21.040
uye kunyanya kune vechidiki iye zvino, sezvo iwe wanunurwa? Ndeipi mazano ako?

0:17:21.040,0:17:26.960
Mazano angu ari zvikuru kuvabereki.

0:17:26.960,0:17:32.440
Vabereki vanofanira kuva ne chekuita pamwe nekuve mune zvekurera kwe vana vavo,

0:17:32.440,0:17:37.260
kwete kungovabereka nekufunga kuti varikuita zvakanaka.

0:17:37.260,0:17:41.860
Kune zvinhu kunze uko izvozvi nokuti dhiyabhorosi anoshandisa chero nzira

0:17:41.860,0:17:46.800
yaanokwanisa kuisa maoko ake kuti aunze vanhu kwaari uye kuti aunze vanhu kurima.

0:17:46.800,0:17:53.200
Vanoshandisa nzira idzi senzira yekuti vagone kubatana nemhuri

0:17:53.200,0:17:58.420
ne kukonzera kuvhiringidzika nezvimwe zvinhu zvinotyisa kumhuri.

0:17:58.420,0:18:00.920
Zano rangu rinoenda kune vabereki kunze uko.

0:18:00.920,0:18:03.240
Vanofanira kunge vakabatana nevana vavo.

0:18:03.240,0:18:08.280
Vanofanira kuziva kuti vana vavo vari kuitei uye kuenda kunzvimbo idzo vana vavo vanoenda.

0:18:08.280,0:18:16.180
Ndinoda kuvonga Mwari kuti Akashandisa izvi senzira yekubata mhuri yangu

0:18:16.180,0:18:22.160
nokuti murikutiona kuti tose tirikunyemwerera, isu tose tirikufara, asi izvi zvanga zvisina kudaro kare.

0:18:22.160,0:18:27.580
Kwemakore makumi maviri nemaviri ekurarama kwangu, handizvo zvazvange zvakaita.

0:18:27.580,0:18:31.620
Iyi ndiyo nguva yokutanga, kwemakore 22 apfuura okuvapo kwangu,

0:18:31.620,0:18:39.060
apo mhuri yasangana pamwe chete, kuva imwechete uye munhu wese ari pano, takakwana.

0:18:39.060,0:18:42.740
Icho chinhu chemufaro kwandiri nokuti ndicho chinhu chandakanga ndichinamatira.

0:18:42.740,0:18:46.460
Ndinotenda Mwari kuti zvazozadziswa muupenyu hwangu.

0:18:46.460,0:18:50.660
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu kamwe zvakare.

0:18:50.660,0:18:57.220
Mukoma wedu ati kekutanga mumakore 22 tinogona kuona mhuri iri pamwe chete, nekuda kwe

0:18:57.220,0:19:00.020
kuponeswa kwake. Tinofara pamwe nemhuri iyi.

0:19:00.020,0:19:02.800
Hatina nguva yekuteerera kune nhengo dzemhuri

0:19:02.800,0:19:04.620
nokuti tine vanhu vakawanda vakamirira kupupurira.

0:19:04.620,0:19:08.680
Tinongoda kukurudzira mhuri iyi, ikozvino sezvo dzikinuro yasvika mumba menyu;

0:19:08.680,0:19:13.260
rambai muchiita kuti Shoko ra Mwari  nhungamiro ye hupenyu hwenyu. Uye zvirokwazvo zvakanakisisa zvichiri kuuya,

0:19:13.260,0:19:14.320
muzita ra Jesu.

